<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Booking Cancelled</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
    .content h2 { color: #333; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 24px; }
    .content p { margin-bottom: 15px; color: #666; }
    .booking-card { background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .booking-card h3 { color: #ef4444; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 18px; }
    .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; }
    .detail-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .detail-label { color: #666; font-weight: 500; }
    .detail-value { color: #333; font-weight: 600; }
    .refund-info { background: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .refund-info p { color: #92400e; margin: 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #fff; padding: 15px 40px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; }
    .footer p { color: #999; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>‚ùå Booking Cancelled</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello {{customerName}},</h2>
      
      <p>Your booking has been cancelled as requested. We're sorry to see you go!</p>

      <div class="booking-card">
        <h3>Cancelled Booking Details</h3>
        
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-label">Booking Number:</span>
          <span class="detail-value">{{bookingNumber}}</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-label">Trip:</span>
          <span class="detail-value">{{tripTitle}}</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-label">Travel Date:</span>
          <span class="detail-value">{{travelDate}}</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-label">Cancellation Date:</span>
          <span class="detail-value">{{cancellationDate}}</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-label">Cancellation Reason:</span>
          <span class="detail-value">{{cancellationReason}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{#if refundAmount}}
      <div class="refund-info">
        <p><strong>üí∞ Refund Information:</strong></p>
        <p>A refund of <strong>${{refundAmount}}</strong> will be processed to your original payment method within 5-10 business days.</p>
        {{#if cancellationFee}}
        <p style="margin-top: 10px;">Cancellation fee: ${{cancellationFee}}</p>
        {{/if}}
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <p>If you cancelled by mistake or have changed your mind, please contact us immediately and we'll do our best to help.</p>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{websiteUrl}}/trips" class="cta-button">Explore More Trips</a>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">We hope to see you again soon for your next adventure!</p>

      <p><strong>The Travellr Team</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} Travellr. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@travellr.com" style="color: #667eea;">support@travellr.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
